data.description: **RECENT PRICE IMPROVEMENT**   Get ready to fall in love! This meticulously maintained pool home in Concord Station is a rare gem that won't last long. With 6 bedrooms, there are endless possibilities for creating your own gym, movie room, or home office space. The home features recently painted interiors and exteriors with ceramic wood tiles downstairs for maximum durability. The luxury chef's kitchen boasts quartz countertops with a glass backsplash, high-end cabinetry, and premium appliances. The living room features an open floor plan with an amazing stonework accent wall that is sure to impress. When you step outside, you are greeted by an outdoor kitchen that makes entertaining easy beside your luxurious, yet low-maintenance, heated saltwater pool with two waterfalls for year-round enjoyment. The first-floor also features a guest bedroom that has access to a fully upgraded bath with granite countertops, and there's a 3-car garage for all your parking and storage needs. Upstairs, you'll find a loft/sitting area centered between 5 large bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms. The spacious primary bedroom has its own sitting area and comes complete with an ensuite luxury bath that has both a relaxing soaking tub and a walk-in shower. The enormous walk-in closet has ample space and includes custom shelving. The Concord Station community features top-of-the-line amenities, including a 5,000 sq ft clubhouse, fitness center, game room, resort-style pool with splash zone, parks, walking and biking trails, playground, basketball, and tennis courts. This breathtaking home and impressive community truly have it all! Located in a prime spot, you can enjoy easy access to shopping, dining, and great schools. Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity. Schedule your showing or personal tour today!
